    </div> 
  </div> 

  
   <div class="w3-row"> 
    <div class="w3-twothird w3-container"> 
      <h3 class="w3-text-teal">2.1</h3>
      <p>Language is a vital aspect of Kadazan-Dusun identity, serving as a unifying force among the diverse subgroups. In recent decades, efforts have been made to standardize the language for educational and cultural purposes. Kadazan-Dusun is now officially recognized as a native language in Malaysia and is taught in schools across Sabah, ensuring its continued relevance for younger generations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-third w3-container"> <div id="2.2"> 
      
      <img src="https://www.theborneopost.com/newsimages/2023/09/email1695548941163WhatsApp-Image-2023-09-24-at-5.37.39-PM.jpeg" alt="Kadazandusun Language" style="width:300px;height:280px;">
    </div>
  </div>

  
  
   <div class="w3-row w3-padding-0">
    <div class="w3-twothird w3-container">
      <h3 class="w3-text-teal">2.2</h3>
      <p>The Kadazan-Dusun language is rich in expressions that reflect the community’s agricultural and spiritual traditions. Words and phrases often carry deep meanings, tied to their reverence for nature, family, and community. Songs, poetry, and oral storytelling play a central role in preserving the language and passing it on to future generations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-third w3-container"> <div id="2.3">
      <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8a/Penampang_Sabah_Kaamatan-Celebrations-2014-01.jpg" alt="Kadazandusun On Stage" style="width:300px;height:280px;">
    </div>
  </div>

  
   
   <div class="w3-row w3-padding-0">
    <div class="w3-twothird w3-container">
      <h3 class="w3-text-teal">2.3</h3>
      <p>Despite its importance, the Kadazan-Dusun language faces challenges in the modern era. The rise of English and Malay as dominant languages in Malaysia has led to a decline in native language usage among the younger population. However, revitalization initiatives, such as language festivals, community classes, and digital resources, are helping to reverse this trend.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-third w3-container"> <div id="2.4"> 
