      <h3 class="w3-text-teal">2.4</h3>
      <p>As a living language, Kadazan-Dusun continues to evolve while maintaining its traditional essence. Its preservation is vital for cultural identity and understanding the worldview and history of the Kadazan-Dusun people. Linguistic preservation efforts highlight the resilience of the community in safeguarding their heritage.</p>
